-Yeah, sure.

16:40.360 --> 16:41.760
Thank you, Vince.

16:44.600 --> 16:46.320
Right.

16:54.400 --> 16:56.240
Looking through a rock star's room.

16:56.280 --> 16:57.760
I'm not so sure about that.

