Okay, so, we look for anything out of the ordinary.

17:27.120 --> 17:29.040
Itemise and bag whatever we find.

17:29.080 --> 17:30.680
Absolutely.

17:30.720 --> 17:32.440
Right, I'll leave this with you.

17:32.480 --> 17:34.400
-Oh. -I'll see you in

17:32.480 --> 17:34.400
