17:42.160 --> 17:45.600
Look, I'm more than happy to swap with you, you know.

17:45.640 --> 17:50.200
But it's the hotel manager. She goes on and on and on.

17:50.240 --> 17:52.840
I wouldn't want you to have to go through that.

17:52.880 --> 17:55.760
No, sir! Not on your first day.

17:57.440 --> 17:58.520
Thank you. You're welcome.

18:03.320 --> 18:04.840
Dwayne Myers.

