So, I tried to find anything from when the band

18:10.480 --> 18:13.560
were here last.

18:13.600 --> 18:16.720
So, <i> The Saint Marie Times</i> are doing a search through

18:13.600 --> 18:16.720
their clippings archive

18:16.760 --> 18:18.360
and will send over anything of interest.

18:18.400 --> 18:20.000
Brilliant. So, suspects?

18:21.000 --> 18:22.120
Pete Thunders.

18:22.160 --> 18:24.400
After the band split, he became an artist.

18:24.440 --> 18:26.520
Having done initial financial checks,

18:26.560 --> 18:28.440
hasn't been very successful.

18:28.480 --> 18:30.720
He has a few cautions on his file, all for assault.

18:30.760 --> 18:33.480
Prone to violence

18:33.520 --> 18:35.400
He retired from music, invested in property

18:35.440 --> 18:37.920
and he's now a millionaire several times over.

18:37.960 --> 18:40.080
So, he's not in this for the money.

18:40.120 --> 18:41.440
Next, Jim Smith.

18:41.480 --> 18:43.240
Had a tempestuous relationship with his brother.

18:43.280 --> 18:44.560
Long history of their bust-ups.

18:44.600 --> 18:46.520
Insisting on separate hotels when touring.

18:46.560 --> 18:48.600
-Usual rock-star stuff.

18:51.000 --> 18:52.360
Er, an e-mail from <i>The Saint Marie Times.</i>

18:52.400 --> 18:54.160
-An attachment.

18:54.200 --> 18:55.400
I'll print it off.

18:55.440 --> 18:58.160
Just leaves us with Cheryl and Vince.

18:58.200 --> 19:00.720
I couldn't find a great deal online about Cheryl.

19:00.760 --> 19:02.960
But, considering she knew Stevie the least,

19:03.000 --> 19:04.880
well, she appeared to be the most upset,

19:04.920 --> 19:06.000
so I'll keep looking.

19:06.040 --> 19:07.400
Vince?

19:07.440 --> 19:10.640
Producer and owner of the recording studio,

19:10.680 --> 19:12.880
originally built by his father in the '60s.

19:12.920 --> 19:14.320
The family business.

19:14.360 --> 19:16.920
Personal life a bit of a mess. Ex-wife lives in London.

19:16.960 --> 19:19.200
Which just leaves us with this little chap.

19:19.240 --> 19:23.320
Why was he found expired at our crime scene,

19:19.240 --> 19:23.320
rather than enjoying life

19:23.360 --> 19:26.880
amongst his fellow click beetles

19:23.360 --> 19:26.880
back on Martinique?

