You should see this.

19:32.560 --> 19:34.920
-It was Vince's studio. -HUMPHREY: Right.

19:42.760 --> 19:45.080
Beer's warm, the food's gone off

19:45.120 --> 19:46.880
and the ice has melted.

19:46.920 --> 19:49.080
What a party, eh?

19:49.120 --> 19:51.440
HUMPHREY: We were wondering if you

19:49.120 --> 19:51.440
had a minute, Mr Thuram.

19:51.480 --> 19:53.200
If that's all it is.

19:53.240 --> 19:55.560
The catering equipment's being flown back early.

19:55.600 --> 19:58.000
I need to get all this lot ready.

19:58.040 --> 20:00.200
HUMPHREY: Hopefully it won't take too long.

20:04.880 --> 20:06.520
Your studio burnt down.

20:09.200 --> 20:11.120
July '91.

20:11.160 --> 20:13.480
The Flowers Of Progress were recording here.

20:17.200 --> 20:20.920
Hmm. It wasn't the greatest of times.

20:20.960 --> 20:23.280
According to the reports, it was Stevie who caused it.

20:23.320 --> 20:25.320
He was at the height of his drinking.

20:25.360 --> 20:27.840
He was reckless. He wouldn't listen to anyone.

20:27.880 --> 20:29.920
He didn't care about anyone else.

20:29.960 --> 20:32.280
So, why did you let them back in?

20:32.320 --> 20:35.120
I didn't want to, believe me.

20:35.160 --> 20:39.320
But I'm not in a position to turn work down, so...

20:39.360 --> 20:41.040
This was your father's studio, wasn't it?

20:41.080 --> 20:42.960
Built it himself.

20:43.000 --> 20:44.160
Must have been particularly upsetting

20:44.200 --> 20:45.960
when the insurance didn't pay out.

20:47.720 --> 20:50.400
It's not been easy, I admit.

20:50.440 --> 20:52.400
But I got through it.

20:52.440 --> 20:54.680
It was three years after the fire

20:54.720 --> 20:56.600
until you were able to reopen the studio.

20:56.640 --> 20:59.400
That's a long time.

20:59.440 --> 21:04.800
Your wife left you during that period, didn't she,

20:59.440 --> 21:04.800
all because of Stevie?

21:04.840 --> 21:08.560
How did you feel, seeing him

21:04.840 --> 21:08.560
after all this time?

21:08.600 --> 21:10.960
Look, the guy's changed.

21:11.000 --> 21:13.200
He's dry now, doesn't touch a drop.

21:13.240 --> 21:17.080
I guess I felt I shouldn't hold it against him.

21:17.120 --> 21:19.440
He's grown up, I suppose.

21:23.240 --> 21:25.000
I'll get those CDs.

21:41.840 --> 21:43.320
Er...

21:43.360 --> 21:46.200
Um, okay, madam, thank you very much.

21:46.240 --> 21:47.560
You've been very helpful.

21:47.600 --> 21:49.960
Now, if you wouldn't mind excusing us, please.

21:53.080 --> 21:55.560
Look, I really wanted to come and help you

21:53.080 --> 21:55.560
with the search, you know.

21:55.600 --> 21:57.000
But I couldn't get away.

21:57.040 --> 21:59.560
That woman could talk a glass eye

21:57.040 --> 21:59.560
to sleep, you know.

21:59.600 --> 22:03.000
So, I itemised and bagged whatever I can find.

22:03.040 --> 22:04.480
Good.

