22:25.720 --> 22:26.760
What?

22:27.560 --> 22:28.960
This.

22:29.000 --> 22:32.080
Stevie's browser history's particularly interesting.

22:33.160 --> 22:34.920
Oh!

22:34.960 --> 22:38.920
<i>-♪ Boo-na-na</i>

