24:44.960 --> 24:47.800
will be terminated

24:47.840 --> 24:51.080
if any of the band defames the product

24:47.840 --> 24:51.080
in print or online.

24:51.120 --> 24:52.840
And this clip is everywhere.

24:52.880 --> 24:55.960
So, Pete stands to lose his share

24:52.880 --> 24:55.960
